author: BuXXe (@dieBuXXe)
title: cine.to
synopsis: Movian plugin to watch cine.to streams
description: cine.to Movian plugin allows the integration of cine.to streams into Movian. cine.to offers a broad variety of german / english movies. If you encounter problems, leave a note at the github. Visit at: https://github.com/BuXXe/movian-cine-plugin
